    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Yes, please use `eth_chainId` rather than `net_version`. Per the [spec](https://github.com/ethereum/execution-apis/blob/main/src/engine/specification.md#underlying-protocol) EL should only expose `engine_` and `eth_` methods on the Engine API port. Erigon doesn't expose `net_` methods by default.",
